TopicTitle: Does anyone have tantares RSS/RO configs?

Articles.Content:
I really like the Tantares parts, but AFAIK they don't seem to have configs for realism overhaul. I looked in the RO folder and they were in the suggested mods, but there was a subfolder for 'new tantares' so I'm guessing something changed at some point re tantares and now there's new configs. Does anyone have new configs for Tantares parts (specifically, Soyuz, TKS, and VA spacecraft)?

Also, unrelated, but I see NO orphan node in my RP1 tech tree. Not, I see one and it is empty - such a node simply does not exist. Any ideas?
I also had this problem when I wanted to try the lunokhod in Tantares. I used the realism overhaul v17.7 and Tantares v5.0, the Tanrares parts are non-ro parts.
